if i am right, you forgot to change the ip on the client when sending it to them.
currently it would be 127.0.0.1 for you which is what you haft to use.
copy the client file and then rename it to like ‘sending file’ so you know which is which and type
in the search “127.0.0.1” and change it to your no-ip. e.g. morparscape.no-ip.biz
